title: Manken.
sinopse:
The story revolves around the main character Higasa Sachi. She's the ideal student who puts on a refined and dignified persona while excelling at sports and academics. She is respected and admired by her peers and teachers alike.

Sachi who cares about appearance can not stand Alice Toyozaki who is a hard core otaku that makes no effort in hiding her love for it. Sachi (who is secretly a budding manga artist) can not understand why Alice puts much effort into drawing manga herself when she has no talent for it, but one day after Alice is picked on by a bully...
